     A*==============================================================
     A* Display File:  JWTCFGD
     A* Description:   Maintenance display file for the JWTCFG table.
     A*                Provides a load-all subfile list view and a
     A*                full-screen detail panel for add/change/view.
     A*
     A* Formats:
     A*   JWTSFLD  – subfile (one JWT config row per line)
     A*   JWTCTL   – subfile control / screen body
     A*   JWTDTL   – full-screen detail panel (add / change / view)
     A*   JWTDEL    – delete confirmation panel
     A*   JWTMSGSFL – message subfile (detail screen errors, row 24)
     A*   JWTMSGCTL – message subfile control (detail screen)
     A*   JWTFOOT   – footer function key legend (row 24, OVERLAY)
     A*
     A* Subfile options:
     A*   2 = Change    4 = Delete    5 = View    9 = Show Public Key
     A*
     A* Function Keys (list):
     A*   F3 = Exit   F5 = Refresh   F6 = Add   F12 = Previous
     A*
     A* Function Keys (detail):
     A*   F12 = Cancel   F10 = Save (add/change only)
     A*
     A* Author:  Generated by GitHub Copilot
     A* Date:    April 4, 2026
     A*==============================================================
     A                                      DSPSIZ(27 132 *DS4)
     A                                      PRINT
     A                                      INDARA
     A*
     A*--------------------------------------------------------------
     A* Record: JWTSFLD – Subfile
     A*   Columns (132-wide):
     A*    2  Opt
     A*    4  JWTID  (5 digits)
     A*   10  JWT Label (36 chars)
     A*   84  Key Label (32 chars)
     A*  117  Key Type (11 chars)
     A*  Note: Key Length and Expiry are visible on the detail screen.
     A*--------------------------------------------------------------
     A          R JWTSFLD                   SFL
     A            SFLRRN         5S 0H
     A            SFLJWTID       5S 0H
     A            SFLOPT         1A  B  9  2VALUES(' ' '2' '4' '5' '9')
     A                                      COLOR(GRN)
     A            SFLJLBL       36A  O  9 10COLOR(GRN)
     A            SFLKSLBL      32A  O  9 84COLOR(GRN)
     A            SFLJWALG      10A  O  9117COLOR(GRN)
     A*
     A*--------------------------------------------------------------
     A* Record: JWTCTL – Subfile Control
     A*--------------------------------------------------------------
     A          R JWTCTL                    SFLCTL(JWTSFLD)
     A                                      SFLSIZ(9999)
     A                                      SFLPAG(13)
     A N90N91                               SFLDSP
     A                                      SFLDSPCTL
     A  90                                  SFLCLR
     A  93                                  SFLEND(*MORE)
     A                                      CF03
     A                                      CF05
     A                                      CF06
     A                                      CF12
     A                                      ROLLUP(25)
     A                                      ROLLDOWN(26)
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A*
     A*  Row 1 – program name, BSL header, date
     A                                  1  2'JWTCFGM'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                  1 57'BSL Subsystem OAUTH'
     A                                      COLOR(YLW)
     A                                  1124DATE
     A                                      EDTCDE(Y)
     A                                      COLOR(GRN)
     A*  Row 2 – screen title, time
     A                                  2 52'JWT Configuration Maintenance'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                      COLOR(YLW)
     A                                  2124TIME
     A                                      COLOR(GRN)
     A*
     A* Row 3 – record count
     A            JWTCOUNT       5S 0O  3  2
     A                                  3  8'record(s)'
     A                                      COLOR(GRN)
     A*
     A* Legend row 4
     A                                  5  2'2=Change  4=Delete  5=View  -
     A                                      9=Show Public Key'
     A                                      COLOR(BLU)
     A*
     A* Column headers – row 6 / 7
     A                                  7  2'Opt'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                  7 10'JWT Label'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                  7 84'Key Label'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                  7117'JWT Alg'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                  8  2'---'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
