     A                                      --'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                  8 84'------------------------'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                  8117'----------'
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A*
     A*--------------------------------------------------------------
     A* Record: JWTDTL – Full-screen detail panel (Add / Change / View)
     A*--------------------------------------------------------------
     A          R JWTDTL
     A                                      CF12
     A                                      CF10
     A                                      CF04
     A                                      ROLLUP(25)
     A                                      ROLLDOWN(26)
     A                                      RTNCSRLOC(&RCD &FLD &POS)
     A                                      CSRLOC(CSRROW CSRCOL)
     A                                      OVERLAY
     A*
     A* Cursor location (returned by RTNCSRLOC on each I/O)
     A            RCD           10A  H
     A            FLD           10A  H
     A            POS            4S 0H
     A* Cursor position (set by program to reposition after F4 prompt)
     A            CSRROW         3S 0H
     A            CSRCOL         3S 0H
     A* Program-to-system attribute fields for validation highlighting
     A            ATTRISS        1A  P
     A            ATTRSUB        1A  P
     A            ATTRAUD        1A  P
     A            ATTREXP        1A  P
     A            ATTRLBL        1A  P
     A            ATTRKSF        1A  P
     A            ATTRKSL        1A  P
     A            ATTRKLB        1A  P
     A            ATTRALG        1A  P
     A*
     A*  Row 1 – program name, BSL header, date
     A                                  1  2'JWTCFGM'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                      COLOR(WHT)
     A                                  1 57'BSL Subsystem OAUTH'
     A                                      COLOR(YLW)
     A                                  1124DATE
     A                                      EDTCDE(Y)
     A                                      COLOR(GRN)
     A*  Row 2 – screen title, time
     A                                  2 52'JWT Configuration Maintenance'
     A                                      DSPATR(HI)
     A                                      COLOR(YLW)
     A                                  2124TIME
     A                                      COLOR(GRN)
     A*  Row 3 – mode indicator (filled by program: 'Add', 'Change', 'View')
     A            DTLMODE        6A  O  3 64DSPATR(HI)
     A*
     A* Fields – the program sets DSPATR(PR) when mode = 'View'
     A* using indicator 92 (protected) controlled via INDARA.
     A*
     A                                  4  2'JWT Label'
